  "initial_text": "Skip to checkout form\n\nNorthstar Goods\n\nGUEST CHECKOUT\n\nNorthstar Goods \u2014 Synthetic checkout demonstration\nAll products, people, contact details, addresses, payment details and order data are fictional and synthetic. Nothing is purchased.\n\nONE-PAGE CHECKOUT\n\nComplete your synthetic order\n\nAll five sections are on this page. Required fields are marked *\nrequired\n.\n\nContact\nDelivery\nShipping\nPayment\nReview\nOrder summary\nAUD 93.50\nNorthstar Insulated Bottle\nQuantity 1\nAUD 32.00\nWillow Cotton Throw\nQuantity 1\nAUD 48.00\nSubtotal\nAUD 80.00\nShipping\nAUD 5.00\nTax\nAUD 8.50\nTotal\nAUD 93.50\nCheckout details\nYour safe progress can be restored after a reload.\nCompact completed sections\n\nOptional: completed sections become short summaries with an Edit button. Every section stays on this page.\n\n1\nContact\n\nFor this fictional delivery only.\n\nContact details\nFull name * \n\nSynthetic value: Alex Morgan.\n\nEmail * \n\nSynthetic value: alex.morgan@example.invalid.\n\nPhone * \n\nSynthetic value: +61 400 000 000.\n\n2\nDelivery address\n\nUse the synthetic Australian address shown below.\n\nDelivery address\nStreet address * \n\nSynthetic value: 42 Fiction Lane.\n\nCity or suburb * \n\nSynthetic value: Sampleton.\n\nState * \n\nSynthetic value: NSW.\n\nPostcode * \n\nSynthetic value: 2000.\n\nCountry * \n\nSynthetic value: Australia.\n\n3\nShipping method\n\nSelect one fictional delivery speed.\n\nComplete\nChoose a shipping method\nStandard \u2014 3 to 5 business days\nAUD 5.00\nExpress \u2014 1 to 2 business days\nAUD 12.00\n4\nSynthetic payment\n\nDemonstration values only. Payment fields are cleared on reload and never saved.\n\nFictional card to use\n4111 1111 1111 1111 \u00b7 expiry 12/34 \u00b7 security code 123 \u00b7 Alex Morgan\nSynthetic card details\nCard number * \n\nUse synthetic digits only. Canonical test value: 4111 1111 1111 1111.\n\nExpiry, MM/YY * \n\nCanonical synthetic test value: 12/34.\n\nSecurity code * \n\nUse 3 or 4 synthetic digits. Canonical test value: 123.\n\nName on card * \n\nCanonical synthetic test value: Alex Morgan.\n\n5\nReview and place order\n\nCheck the fictional details before the local confirmation.\n\nReview confirmation\nContact and delivery\n\nEnter your synthetic contact and address above.\n\nEdit contact\nShipping and payment\n\nStandard \u2014 3 to 5 business days \u00b7 AUD 5.00\n\nPayment: synthetic card ending 1111 after entry; payment details are not saved.\n\nEdit shipping Edit payment\nI reviewed the fictional order and understand that Place order creates only a local synthetic confirmation.\n\nRequired before the local demonstration can finish.\n\nDue now\nAUD 93.50\nPlace order\nLocal, network-free accessibility prototype \u00b7 fictional and synthetic data only",
